Paper: hep-th/0106187

Date: 2001-06-20

Title: String Field Theory and the Fuzzy Sphere

Authors: Harald Ita and Yaron Oz

Comments: 14 pages, Latex, typos corrected, ref. added

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B519 (2001) 129-136

We use boundary string field theory to study open string tachyon condensationon a three-sphere closed string background. We consider the closed stringbackground described by $SU(2)_k$ WZW model in the limit of large $k$. Wecompute the exact tachyon potential and analyse the decay modes.